trans-unit.source: Represents the method that is called when an <xref href="System.Activities.ActivityDelegate"></xref> completes.
trans-unit.target: 表示时，将调用的方法<xref href="System.Activities.ActivityDelegate"></xref>完成。

trans-unit.source: The values in the `outArguments` dictionary are the <xref:System.Activities.ActivityDelegateParameter> values of the <xref:System.Activities.ActivityDelegate> that are assigned when the <xref:System.Activities.ActivityDelegate> is invoked, keyed by <xref:System.Activities.ActivityDelegateParameter.Name%2A>.
trans-unit.target: 中的值`outArguments`字典<xref:System.Activities.ActivityDelegateParameter>值<xref:System.Activities.ActivityDelegate>分配时<xref:System.Activities.ActivityDelegate>调用，由<xref:System.Activities.ActivityDelegateParameter.Name%2A>.</xref:System.Activities.ActivityDelegateParameter.Name%2A>键控</xref:System.Activities.ActivityDelegate></xref:System.Activities.ActivityDelegate></xref:System.Activities.ActivityDelegateParameter>
